二、指定教科書及參考資料 Textbooks and Reference(請修課同學遵守智慧財產權，不得非法影印)


●指定教科書 Required TextsPhillip Areeda & Louis Kaplow, Antitrust Analysis: Problems, Text, Cases (2004) and supplements (2010).
		●參考書資料暨網路資源 Reference Books and Online Resources


三、教學目標 Objectives


本課程討論公平交易法特殊問題，著重於公平交易法與智慧財產權的融合與衝突，並藉由國內外案例說明。 


This course analyzes both US antitrust law and Taiwan fair trade act through investigating related cases. Topics include horizontal agreements in restraint of trade, monopolization, vertical exclusionary agreements, vertical distributional restraints, price discrimination, mergers, and the interface of intellectual property and competition. 


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall Description1. General remark2. Introduction to Antitrust economics3. Introduction to US antitrust law4. Introduction to Taiwan Fair trade Act5. Case Study: Standard Oil Co. v. United States6. Case Study: Dr. Miles Medical Co. v. John D. Park & Sons Co.7. Case Study: United States v. Socony-Vacuum8. Case Study: United States v. Aluminum Co. of America9. Cases Study: United States v. Arnold Schwinn & Co. and Continental TV Inc. v. GTE Sylvania Inc.10. Case Study: United States v. Topco Associates, Inc.11. Case Study: Broadcast Music, Inc. v. Columbia Broadcasting System, Inc.12. Case Study: Aspen Skiing 13. Case Study: Superior Court Trail lawyers 14. Case Study: United States v. Microsoft15. Case Study: Federal Trade Commission v. Staples16. GE/Honeywell17. Conclusion

